{"tid":530881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼肥色狼現荃灣 梯間非禮14歲女","createTime":"2018-01-16T08:33:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T08:46:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4571c9d4b9883902746c4be88b42650994005f","tid":530881,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:33:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180116/20276144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F20276144&d=X9IW%2BGPfmw1%2FZ%2F0ymGgNcP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f311d3fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180116%2F20276144&h=2054fdac\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180116/20276144</a><br />\n<br />\n四眼肥色狼現荃灣<br />\n梯間非禮14歲女<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】荃灣有色狼出現！昨午2時許，14歲女童行經四坡坊一大廈梯間時，遭一名中年男子尾隨及非禮，她事後告知母親，由母親代為報案。警方經初步調查，案件列作非禮，交由荃灣警區刑事調查隊跟進，暫未有人被捕，正追緝一名年約40至50歲的男子，約1.7米高，肥身材，蓄短髮，戴眼鏡，案發時身穿黑色外套及黑色長褲。"},{"pid":"72b5540f705037a1a0ec883d71630c20b19b331d","tid":530881,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:46:06.000Z","msg":"點非禮法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}